{"title":"故乡故乡","authors":["查干"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":7,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"查干（蒙古族）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎鲁特的杏树林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎鲁特的杏树林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总来染亮游子的梦境"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呓语一声披衣而坐时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杏花的四月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已不期而至"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是在泪溪之外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斜照的日光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一种无奈和期待"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉红的空气四处漫溢时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡的山野皆为芬芳的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相思不敢去叩?亥吐村那扇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月下的柴门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈的长咳会惊扰游子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦中的窥探"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更不敢去读余光中先生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一首泣鬼神的《乡愁》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯恐在清明祭扫的路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"误入歧途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得倾诉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝色的蒙古"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖先示我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝色是我们的图腾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崇拜蓝色就是崇拜上苍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝色的蒙古"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一只起飞于海边的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍鸢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地展开一条蓝缎子哈达"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如我们灵魂之帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果你嗅到大海之体味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么二月兰的激情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将会在漠风中撒网"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今蓝色的梦已在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马背上成型"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝色的炊烟也将一种信息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种植荒原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更有一种植物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在积年的干旱中生长着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那便是我们蓝色的祈愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在漫长的牧放中经受磨练"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"征驼漫日漫月地嚼着它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将尖剌嚼成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"簇新的日月和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长翎的歌谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夜京都"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星灯如珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大钟寺的晚钟荡漾有声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天是你的生日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的内蒙古"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夜我守于高高的星野斋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你去迎迓又一轮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乳香的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝阳"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}